node.text:
One of the finest examples of modern architecture on a prime corner lot, in the heart of the Beverly Hills flats. .
527 N Palm Drive.
Beverly Hills, CA 90210
11,438 Square Feet
6 Bedrooms
11 Bathrooms
Movie Theater
Fitness Center 
Sauna & Steam Shower
.
Listed by: @AaronKirman 
Price: $19,995,000.00
.
.
For more listings, check out @AaronKirman page! .
.
